{"tid":1164424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】林鄭：外部勢力令議題提升至一國兩制層面　中央發言理所當然 (10:23)","createTime":"2019-05-21T05:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T15:33:17.000Z","uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"10a5091823ce67bd03ea382518b2273777b76a51","tid":1164424,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190521/s00001/726cf034e4002e7c1b584d148b6fb01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190521%2Fs00001%2F726cf034e4002e7c1b584d148b6fb01a.jpg&h=5995c778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局長李家超昨（20日）提出將《逃犯條例》修訂「直上大會」，引起爭議。特首林鄭月娥今早（21日）出席行會前見記者，形容決定艱難，強調政府是為了打破困局。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，港府尊重立法會功能，明白經過法案委員會審議的草案會有更好結果，但經過法案委員會多次爭議後，不但寶貴審議時間已經喪失，甚至看不到前路，故政府為打破困局作出此決定。她承諾未來政務司、律政司、保安局等都會加強解說，以釋除公眾疑慮，希望事件不會影響未來各黨派關係。<br />\n<br />\n至於台灣當局表明不會借修例引渡陳同佳，林鄭月娥認為若未有法律基礎便與申請移交的一方商議，並非穩妥做法，強調修例後政府會以最大誠意，基於「伸張正義」這一共同目標與對方磋商。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又稱，不少後期加入的針對修例言論，涉及外部勢力，甚至有人借此影響中央與香港關係，甚至肆意抨擊內地法律制度，令議題提升至「一國兩制」和憲制層面，因此中央發言理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190521/s00001/1558405430182/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad-%e5%a4%96%e9%83%a8%e5%8b%a2%e5%8a%9b%e4%bb%a4%e8%ad%b0%e9%a1%8c%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%a9%e5%88%b6%e5%b1%a4%e9%9d%a2-%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e7%99%bc%e8%a8%80%e7%90%86%e6%89%80%e7%95%b6%e7%84%b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190521%2Fs00001%2F1558405430182%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad-%25e5%25a4%2596%25e9%2583%25a8%25e5%258b%25a2%25e5%258a%259b%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e9%25a1%258c%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%258d%2587%25e8%2587%25b3%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%2588%25b6%25e5%25b1%25a4%25e9%259d%25a2-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25ae%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%25a8%2580%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%2589%2580%25e7%2595%25b6%25e7%2584%25b6&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=7a3d9534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190521%2Fs00001%2F1558405430182%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad-%25e5%25a4%2596%25e9%2583%25a8%25e5%258b%25a2%25e5%258a%259b%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e9%25a1%258c%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%258d%2587%25e8%2587%25b3%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%2588%25b6%25e5%25b1%25a4%25e9%259d%25a2-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25ae%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%25a8%2580%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%2589%2580%25e7%2595%25b6%25e7%2584%25b6&h=ad84f759\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190521/s00001/1558405430182/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad-%e5%a4%96%e9%83%a8%e5%8b%a2%e5%8a%9b%e4%bb%a4%e8%ad%b0%e9%a1%8c%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%a9%e5%88%b6%e5%b1%a4%e9%9d%a2-%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e7%99%bc%e8%a8%80%e7%90%86%e6%89%80%e7%95%b6%e7%84%b6</a>"},{"pid":"07ab7f73d96695548ceb601c547be40285c5ecd4","tid":1164424,"uid":40763,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"呢條鳩閪 日日中央中央 我屌你老母臭化閪 睇到你就眼火爆 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"41a61dacb28a982a424da10372ba30b2c2719c22","tid":1164424,"uid":59570,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"希望林鄭全家生癌死"},{"pid":"4f7c8a27330aaa03fef23b3e696a109145943092","tid":1164424,"uid":133680,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"14年如果佢渣旗應該出左解放軍，佢咁無能又無統治意志"},{"pid"